    "last_activity_date" : 1626573419,
    "creation_date" : 1626573419,
    "answer_id" : 68425452,
    "question_id" : 7642456,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Update on version Intellij IDEA 2020.2.3</p>\n<p><code>Settings -&gt; Build,Execution,Deployment -&gt; Build Tools -&gt; Maven -&gt; Importing</code>\nand click &quot;<strong>create module groups for multi-module Maven projects</strong>&quot;.</p>\n<p>Then Apply and you can see that option in &quot;Add Framework Support...&quot;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/4ye4x.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/4ye4x.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n"
  }, {
