    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Using IntelliJ Idea 2022.3.3, here is the easiest way you can do it:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Right click on root of your project in Explorer on the left side.</li>\n<li>Select &quot;Add framework support&quot; (3rd option from the last as shown in image)</li>\n<li>Choose Maven\n<a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/QlaG7.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/QlaG7.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></li>\n</ul>\n"
